.Dd May 14, 2024
.Dt RVN-ALIAS 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm "rvn alias"
.Nd display configured aliases
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl q
.Op Fl l
.Op Ar alias
.Pp
.Nm "rvn alias"
.Op Fl -quiet
.Op Fl -list
.Op Ar alias
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
displays configured aliases.
The alias list can be displayed with or without arguments and column headers.
.Sh OPTIONS
The following options are supported by
.Nm :
.Bl -tag -width quiet
.It Fl l , Fl -list
Print all aliases, one alias per line, without their arguments.
.It Fl q , Fl -quiet
Force quiet output (suppress column headers).
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
Display all aliases:
.Dl % rvn alias
.Pp
Display
.Xr rvn 8
for alias
.Dq Li size :
.Dl % rvn alias size
